{"type":"message","id":"4064f5c5","parentId":"78981d8e","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:17:08.301Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. If BOOTSTRAP.md exists in the provided Project Context, read it and follow its instructions first. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Monday, July 6th, 2026 - 23:17 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-07-06 15:17 UTC"}],"timestamp":1783351028299}}
{"type":"message","id":"02981c45","parentId":"4064f5c5","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:17:16.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me execute the session startup sequence by reading the required files as specified in AGENTS.md.\n\nI need to read:\n1. ~/self-improving/memory.md (HOT layer)\n2. ~/proactivity/memory.md\n3. .learnings/ERRORS.md (last 10 entries)\n\nLet me also check if there's a BOOTSTRAP.md.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_43779673d1e84dd9ba542373","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\BOOTSTRAP.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_963f71b19db6436997afb022","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\self-improving\\memory.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9ee97c6eec144628b33eb2fb","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\proactivity\\memory.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6a4764bf919845b986364e32","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\.learnings\\ERRORS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":17513,"output":170,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17683,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783351028302,"responseId":"cht000d670d@dx19f380134c329c2503"}}
