{"type":"message","id":"ddd48a31","parentId":"f66cde77","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:26:30.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，replay.html里的完整调用链：\n\n1. refreshFiles() → refreshFiles:\n```javascript\nwindow.refreshFiles=function(){\n    fetch('/api/v1/files/list').then(function(r){return r.json()}).then(function(result){\n        if(result.success){allData=result.data.groups||[];updateDateTree();showThumbnails('')}\n    });\n};\n```\n\n2. refreshFiles 调用 showThumbnails:\n\n```javascript\nwindow.showThumbnails=function(date,filterType){\n    items.sort(function(a,b){return sortDesc?(b.date||'').localeCompare(a.date||''):(a.date||'').localeCompare(b.date||'')});\n    document.getElementById('replay-count').textContent=items.length;\n    var c=document.getElementById('replay-grid');\n    if(!items.length){c.innerHTML='<div class=\"replay-empty\"><div class=\"replay-empty-icon\">📂</div><div>暂无文件</div></div>';return}\n    c.innerHTML=items.map(function(item){\n        var url='/api/v1/files/serve/'+encodeURIComponent(item.file);\n        var thumb=item.type==='video'?('/api/v1/files/thumb/'+encodeURIComponent(item.file)):url;  // ← 点击的缩略图\n        ...\n        if(item.type==='video'){\n            fetch('/api/v1/files/info/'+encodeURIComponent(item.file)).then(function(r){return r.json()}).then(function(info){\n                ...\n            });\n        }\n    }).join('');\n\n\n```\n\n点击缩略图时，会处理图片或视频预览。对于视频，会触发额外的信息获取和预览模态框的创建。还有一个日期筛选和排序功能，可以灵活控制文件显示方式。\n\n```\n\njavascript\n// 复选框和删除功能实现\nfunction toggleSelect(file, el) {\n    ...\n\nfunction deleteSelected()  ...\n}\n```\n\n文件的预处理和配置选项涉及路径处理和网络请求。`processFileParams()`可能像playback.html那样辅助URL编码，处理文件路径的转换和规范化。\n\n需要继续追踪replay.html中showThumbnails调用的完整上下文，看看processFileParams的具体应用。根据上下文，可能是前端对文件路径进行进一步处理。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查整个调用链，看是否有重复请求："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1021c6f6d5214b73b8cf216b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\replay.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":48263,"output":483,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48746,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783351562266,"responseId":"cht000dc345@dx19f38095f932872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d6976ae","parentId":"ddd48a31","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:26:30.125Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1021c6f6d5214b73b8cf216b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        <!-- ==================== 回放页面 v7.105 ==================== -->\n        <div class=\"page\" id=\"page-replay\">\n            <div class=\"replay-layout\">\n                <div class=\"replay-sidebar\">\n                    <div class=\"sidebar-header\">\n                        <span>媒体库</span>\n                        <button class=\"sidebar-btn\" onclick=\"openRecordFolder()\" title=\"打开目录\">📂</button>\n                        <button class=\"sidebar-btn\" onclick=\"refreshFiles()\" title=\"刷新\">🔄</button>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"sidebar-tree\" id=\"replay-tree\">\n                        <div class=\"tree-node\">\n                            <div class=\"tree-label active\" onclick=\"toggleAll()\">\n                                <span class=\"tree-arrow open\" id=\"arrow-all\">▼</span>\n                                <span>全部文件</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"tree-children\" id=\"children-all\" style=\"display:block\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"replay-main\">\n                    <div class=\"replay-header\">\n                        <span id=\"replay-title\">全部文件</span>\n                        <span id=\"replay-count\" class=\"replay-count-badge\">0</span>\n                        <div class=\"header-spacer\"></div>\n                        <button class=\"header-btn\" onclick=\"toggleSelectMode()\" id=\"btn-select\">多选</button>\n                        <button class=\"header-btn\" onclick=\"filterFiles()\" id=\"btn-filter\">筛选</button>\n                        <button class=\"header-btn\" onclick=\"sortFiles()\" id=\"btn-sort\">排序</button>\n                        <button class=\"header-btn danger\" onclick=\"deleteSelected()\" id=\"btn-delete\">删除</button>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"replay-grid\" id=\"replay-grid\">\n                        <div class=\"replay-empty\"><div class=\"replay-empty-icon\">📂</div><div>点击刷新加载文件</div></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <style>\n        .replay-layout{display:flex;min-height:600px}\n        .replay-sidebar{width:200px;background:#161b22;border-right:1px solid #21262d;flex-shrink:0;overflow-y:auto}\n        .sidebar-header{font-size:14px;padding:8px 12px;color:#58a6ff;border-bottom:1px solid #21262d;font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}\n        .sidebar-btn{background:#21262d;border:none;color:#8b949e;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px}\n        .sidebar-btn:hover{background:#30363d;color:#e0e6f0}\n        .sidebar-tree{padding:4px 0}\n        .tree-label{padding:10px 12px;color:#8b949e;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}\n        .tree-label:hover{background:#21262d;color:#e0e6f0}\n        .tree-label.active{background:#238636;color:#fff}\n        .tree-arrow{font-size:10px;width:14px;text-align:center}\n        .tree-children{}\n        .tree-date{padding:8px 12px 8px 26px;color:#8b949e;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between}\n        .tree-date:hover{background:#21262d;color:#e0e6f0}\n        .tree-date.active{background:#30363d;color:#58a6ff}\n        .replay-main{flex:1;min-width:0;padding:16px;overflow-y:auto;background:#0d1117}\n        .replay-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #21262d;margin-bottom:16px}\n        #replay-title{font-size:16px;color:#e0e6f0}\n        .replay-count-badge{font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;background:#21262d;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px}\n        .header-spacer{flex:1}\n        .header-btn{background:#21262d;border:none;color:#8b949e;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px}\n        .header-btn:hover{background:#30363d;color:#e0e6f0}\n        .header-btn.danger{color:#f85149}\n        .header-btn.danger:hover{background:#f8514922}\n        .replay-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:12px}\n        .replay-item{background:#161b22;border:1px solid #21262d;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .2s;position:relative}\n        .replay-item:hover{border-color:#58a6ff}\n        .replay-item.selected{border-color:#238636;background:#23863622}\n        .replay-item-checkbox{position:absolute;top:8px;left:8px;width:20px;height:20px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;display:none;z-index:10}\n        .replay-item-checkbox.visible{display:block}\n        .replay-item-checkbox.checked{background:#238636;border-color:#238636}\n        .replay-thumb{width:100%;height:100px;object-fit:cover;display:block;background:#21262d}\n        .replay-thumb-video{width:100%;height:100px;background:#21262d;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#6e7681;font-size:32px;position:relative}\n        .replay-info-overlay{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:linear-gradient(transparent,rgba(0,0,0,.8));padding:24px 6px 4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;pointer-events:none}\n        .replay-info-icon{font-size:14px}\n        .replay-info-text{font-size:10px;color:#fff}\n        .replay-item-info{padding:6px 8px}\n        .replay-item-name{font-size:11px;color:#e0e6f0;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}\n        .replay-item-time{font-size:10px;color:#6e7681;margin-top:2px}\n        .replay-empty{text-align:center;padding:60px 20px;color:#6e7681}\n        .replay-empty-icon{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:12px}\n        .replay-modal{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,.85);z-index:9999;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center}\n        .replay-modal.active{display:flex}\n        .replay-modal-img{max-width:90vw;max-height:90vh;object-fit:contain}\n        .replay-modal-video{max-width:90vw;max-height:90vh}\n        .replay-modal-close{position:absolute;top:16px;right:16px;background:#21262d;border:none;color:#e0e6f0;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;font-size:18px;z-index:10000}\n        </style>\n        \n        <script>\n        (function(){\n            var allData=[],currentDate='',selectMode=false,selectedFiles={},sortDesc=true;\n            \n            window.initReplayPage=function(){refreshFiles()};\n            \n            window.openRecordFolder=function(){\n                fetch('/api/v1/files/open-folder',{method:'POST'}).then(function(r){return r.json()});\n            };\n            \n            window.refreshFiles=function(){\n                fetch('/api/v1/files/list').then(function(r){return r.json()}).then(function(result){\n                    if(result.success){allData=result.data.groups||[];updateDateTree();showThumbnails('')}\n                });\n            };\n            \n            window.toggleAll=function(){\n                var c=document.getElementById('children-all'),a=document.getElementById('arrow-all');\n                c.style.display=c.style.display==='block'?'none':'block';\n                a.classList.toggle('open');\n            };\n            \n            window.selectDate=function(date){\n                currentDate=date;\n                document.querySelectorAll('.tree-date').forEach(function(e){e.classList.remove('active')});\n                var d=document.querySelector('.tree-date[data-date=\"'+date+'\"]');\n                if(d)d.classList.add('active');\n                document.getElementById('replay-title').textContent=date||'全部文件';\n                showThumbnails(date);\n            };\n            \n            window.toggleSelectMode=function(){\n                selectMode=!selectMode;\n                document.getElementById('btn-select').textContent=selectMode?'取消':'多选';\n                document.getElementById('btn-delete').style.display=selectMode?'inline-block':'none';\n                document.querySelectorAll('.replay-item-checkbox').forEach(function(e){e.classList.toggle('visible',selectMode)});\n                if(!selectMode)selectedFiles={};\n            };\n            \n            window.toggleSelect=function(file,el){\n                if(selectedFiles[file]){delete selectedFiles[file];el.classList.remove('checked')}\n                else{selectedFiles[file]=true;el.classList.add('checked')}\n                var item=el.closest('.replay-item');\n                item.classList.toggle('selected',!!selectedFiles[file]);\n            };\n            \n            window.deleteSelected=function(){\n                var files=Object.keys(selectedFiles);\n                if(files.length===0)return;\n                showModal({\n                    type:'confirm',\n                    title:'删除文件',\n                    message:'确定删除 '+files.length+' 个文件吗？',\n                    onConfirm:function(){\n                        fetch('/api/v1/files/delete',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify({files:files})})\n                        .then(function(r){return r.json()}).then(function(result){\n                            if(result.success){selectedFiles={};refreshFiles()}\n                        });\n                    }\n                });\n            };\n            \n            window.sortFiles=function(){\n                sortDesc=!sortDesc;\n                document.getElementById('btn-sort').textContent=sortDesc?'倒序':'正序';\n                showThumbnails(currentDate);\n            };\n            \n            window.filterFiles=function(){\n                showModal({\n                    type:'form',\n                    title:'筛选文件',\n                    fields:[{id:'filterType',label:'类型 (image / video / all)',value:'all',placeholder:'image / video / all'}],\n                    onConfirm:function(data){\n                        var type=(data.filterType||'').trim();\n                        if(!type)return;\n                        showThumbnails(currentDate,type);\n                    }\n                });\n            };\n            \n            function updateDateTree(){\n                var c=document.getElementById('children-all');\n                if(!allData.length){c.innerHTML='<div style=\"padding:8px 12px 8px 26px;color:#6e7681;font-size:12px\">暂无文件</div>';return}\n                c.innerHTML=allData.map(function(g){\n                    return'<div class=\"tree-date\" data-date=\"'+g.date+'\" onclick=\"selectDate(\\''+g.date+'\\')\"><span>'+g.date+'</span><span>'+(g.items?g.items.length:0)+'</span></div>'\n                }).join('');\n            }\n            \n            function showThumbnails(date,filterType){\n                var items=[];\n                if(date){var g=allData.find(function(x){return x.date===date});if(g)items=g.items||[]}\n                else{allData.forEach(function(g){if(g.items)items=items.concat(g.items)})}\n                if(filterType&&filterType!=='all')items=items.filter(function(i){return i.type===filterType});\n                items.sort(function(a,b){return sortDesc?(b.date||'').localeCompare(a.date||''):(a.date||'').localeCompare(b.date||'')});\n                document.getElementById('replay-count').textContent=items.length;\n                var c=document.getElementById('replay-grid');\n                if(!items.length){c.innerHTML='<div class=\"replay-empty\"><div class=\"replay-empty-icon\">📂</div><div>暂无文件</div></div>';return}\n                c.innerHTML=items.map(function(item){\n                    var url='/api/v1/files/serve/'+encodeURIComponent(item.file);\n                    var thumb=item.type==='video'?('/api/v1/files/thumb/'+encodeURIComponent(item.file)):url;\n                    var name=item.file.split('/')[1]||item.file;\n                    var time=(item.date||'').substring(11);\n                    var icon=item.type==='image'?'🖼️':'🎬';\n                    if(item.type==='image'){\n                        return'<div class=\"replay-item\" data-file=\"'+item.file+'\">'+\n                        '<div class=\"replay-item-checkbox'+(selectMode?' visible':'')+(selectedFiles[item.file]?' checked':'')+'\" onclick=\"toggleSelect(\\''+item.file+'\\',this)\"></div>'+\n                        '<div style=\"position:relative\">'+\n                        '<img class=\"replay-thumb\" src=\"'+thumb+'\" loading=\"lazy\" onclick=\"showPreview(\\''+url+'\\',\\'image\\')\">'+\n                        '<div class=\"replay-info-overlay\"><span class=\"replay-info-icon\">'+icon+'</span></div></div>'+\n                        '<div class=\"replay-item-info\"><div class=\"replay-item-name\">'+name+'</div><div class=\"replay-item-time\">'+time+'</div></div></div>'\n                    }else{\n                        return'<div class=\"replay-item\" data-file=\"'+item.file+'\">'+\n                        '<div class=\"replay-item-checkbox'+(selectMode?' visible':'')+(selectedFiles[item.file]?' checked':'')+'\" onclick=\"toggleSelect(\\''+item.file+'\\',this)\"></div>'+\n                        '<div style=\"position:relative\">'+\n                        '<img class=\"replay-thumb\" src=\"'+thumb+'\" loading=\"lazy\" onclick=\"showPreview(\\''+url+'\\',\\'video\\')\">'+\n                        '<div class=\"replay-info-overlay\"><span class=\"replay-info-icon\">'+icon+'</span><span class=\"replay-info-text\" id=\"dur-'+item.file.replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9]/g,'x')+'\"></span></div></div>'+\n                        '<div class=\"replay-item-info\"><div class=\"replay-item-name\">'+name+'</div><div class=\"replay-item-time\">'+time+'</div></div></div>'\n                    }\n                }).join('');\n                // Load video durations\n                items.forEach(function(item){\n                    if(item.type==='video'){\n                        var id='dur-'+item.file.replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9]/g,'x');\n                        fetch('/api/v1/files/info/'+encodeURIComponent(item.file)).then(function(r){return r.json()}).then(function(info){\n                            if(info.success&&info.data.duration){\n                                var el=document.getElementById(id);\n                                if(el)el.textContent=info.data.duration;\n                            }\n                        });\n                    }\n                });\n            }\n            \n            window.showPreview=function(url,type){\n                if(selectMode)return;\n                var m=document.getElementById('replay-modal');\n                if(!m){m=document.createElement('div');m.id='replay-modal';m.className='replay-modal';m.onclick=function(e){if(e.target===m)closeReplayModal()};document.body.appendChild(m)}\n                m.innerHTML=type==='image'\n                    ?'<button class=\"replay-modal-close\" onclick=\"closeReplayModal()\">×</button><img class=\"replay-modal-img\" src=\"'+url+'\">'\n                    :'<button class=\"replay-modal-close\" onclick=\"closeReplayModal()\">×</button><video class=\"replay-modal-video\" controls autoplay src=\"'+url+'\"></video>';\n                m.classList.add('active');\n            };\n            \n            window.closeReplayModal=function(){\n                var m=document.getElementById('replay-modal');\n                if(m){var v=m.querySelector('video');if(v){v.pause();v.src=''}m.classList.remove('active')}\n            };\n            \n            document.addEventListener('keydown',function(e){if(e.key==='Escape')closeReplayModal()});\n        })();\n        </script>\n        <!-- ==================== 首次连接引导向导 ==================== -->\n    </div>"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783351590125}}
{"type":"message","id":"617a1bc3","parentId":"6d6976ae","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:27:19.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在让我检查 `serve_file` 是否有 Range 支持问题，以及 `FileResponse` 的行为："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_694e40a2b9e9454085b6f40d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1832,"path":"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":51846,"output":55,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783351590126,"responseId":"cht000def4e@dx19f380a37aa29bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2032791e","parentId":"617a1bc3","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:27:19.324Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_694e40a2b9e9454085b6f40d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.get(\"/files/serve/{filename:path}\", summary=\"提供文件访问\", tags=[\"Files\"])\r\nasync def serve_file(filename: str):\r\n    \"\"\"v7.105: 提供文件直接访问(流式传输,零内存占用).\"\"\"\r\n    from pathlib import Path\r\n    from fastapi.responses import FileResponse\r\n\r\n    record_path = _resolve_storage_path()\r\n    file_path = Path(record_path) / filename\r\n\r\n    if not file_path.exists():\r\n        return JSONResponse(status_code=404, content={\"success\": False, \"message\": \"文件不存在\"})\r\n\r\n    return FileResponse(\r\n        path=str(file_path),\r\n        filename=file_path.name,\r\n        media_type=_guess_mime(file_path.suffix.lower()),\r\n    )\r\n\r\n\r\ndef _guess_mime(ext: str) -> str:\r\n    \"\"\"v7.105: 根据扩展名猜 MIME 类型.\"\"\"\r\n    mime_map = {\r\n        '.jpg': 'image/jpeg', '.jpeg': 'image/jpeg',\r\n        '.png': 'image/png', '.gif': 'image/gif',\r\n        '.mp4': 'video/mp4', '.avi': 'video/x-msvideo',\r\n        '.mov': 'video/quicktime', '.mkv': 'video/x-matroska',\r\n    }\r\n    return mime_map.get(ext, 'application/octet-stream')\r\n\r\n\r\n\n[2446 more lines in file. Use offset=1862 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783351639324}}
