{"type":"message","id":"f6d8cc65","parentId":"0afe5c16","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:51:23.966Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_551f040049864fffae460783","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function consoleSnapshot() {\r\n            if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n                showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            var deviceIp = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n            var btn = document.getElementById('btnConsoleSnapshot');\r\n            btn.disabled = true;\r\n            btn.textContent = '抓取中...';\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/capture', null).then(function(result) {\r\n                btn.disabled = false;\r\n                btn.textContent = '📷 截图';\r\n                if (result && result.success) {\r\n                    showToast('success', '截图成功: ' + (result.data && result.data.filename || ''));\r\n                    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('截图', 'success');\r\n                    var timeStr = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour12: false });\r\n                    if (typeof mediaLog === 'function') mediaLog(timeStr + ' 截图成功', 'success');\r\n                } else {\r\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : '截图失败');\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                btn.disabled = false;\r\n                btn.textContent = '📷 截图';\r\n                showToast('error', '截图异常: ' + e.message);\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        // 录像 (主控台版) - v7.110: WASM录制 + 自动上传 + 30分钟分割\r\n        var _recordSegmentTimer = null;  // 30分钟分割定时器\r\n        var _recordSegmentAuto = false;  // 是否自动分割\r\n\r\n        function consoleRecordStart(autoRestart) {\r\n            if (!WasmPlayer || !WasmPlayer.playing) {\r\n                showToast('warning', '请先开始预览');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n            var deviceName = (dev && (dev.name || dev.device_name || dev.ip) || 'device').replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9\\u4e00-\\u9fa5_-]/g, '_');\r\n            var now = new Date();\r\n            var dateStr = now.getFullYear() + String(now.getMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0') + String(now.getDate()).padStart(2,'0');\r\n            var timeStr = String(now.getHours()).padStart(2,'0') + String(now.getMinutes()).padStart(2,'0') + String(now.getSeconds()).padStart(2,'0');\r\n\n[1227 more lines in file. Use offset=1880 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783353083966}}
{"type":"message","id":"5332c6a5","parentId":"f6d8cc65","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:52:08.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"截图使用 `/api/v1/ptz/{ip}/capture`（ISAPI API），通过 `wasmCapturePic` -> I2_CapturePic 保存到浏览器下载目录。\n\n现在让我更新 /files/upload-record 端点，让它在保存文件后自动生成缩略图和元数据。\n\n关键点：文件已保存到 `astrohub/storage/YYYY-MM-DD/filename`，然后需要为这个视频文件生成 .thumb.jpg 和 .meta.json。\n\n我需要使用 ffmpeg 和 ffprobe。这两个命令在 router.py 中已经有使用了。\n\n代码逻辑：\n1. 文件保存完成后\n2. 检查文件类型（只有视频需要缩略图）\n3. 如果是视频：\n   - 提取第一帧：`ffmpeg -i video.mp4 -vframes 1 -q:v 5 thumb.jpg`\n   - 提取元数据：`ffprobe -v quiet -print_format json ...`\n   - 保存 .meta.json\n4. 返回成功响应\n\n需要处理的异常：\n- ffmpeg/ffprobe 不存在\n- 处理失败\n- 权限问题\n\n让我开始修改 /files/upload-record 端点。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"开始修改 `/files/upload-record` 端点，让它在保存文件后自动生成缩略图和元数据："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_66b5673c2c7545fb98a43c5f","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"@api_router.post(\"/files/upload-record\", summary=\"接收录像文件，保存后自动生成缩略图和元数据\", tags=[\"Files\"])\nasync def upload_record(request: Request) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"v7.119: 上传录像文件到服务器，自动生成缩略图和元数据。\"\"\"\n    from pathlib import Path\n    from datetime import datetime\n    from fastapi import UploadFile\n    import shutil\n    import json\n    import subprocess\n    import os\n\n    try:\n        form = await request.form()\n        file: UploadFile = form.get(\"file\")\n        if not file:\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"未收到文件\"}\n\n        record_path = _resolve_storage_path()\n        date_str = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n        date_dir = Path(record_path) / date_str\n        date_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n        filepath = date_dir / file.filename\n        with open(filepath, \"wb\") as f:\n            shutil.copyfileobj(file.file, f)\n\n        # 自动生成缩略图和元数据\n        ext = filepath.suffix.lower()\n        if ext in ['.mp4', '.avi', '.mov', '.mkv']:\n            # 生成缩略图\n            thumb_file = filepath.with_suffix('.thumb.jpg')\n            if not thumb_file.exists():\n                try:\n                    subprocess.run([\n                        'ffmpeg', '-y', '-ss', '1', '-i', str(filepath),\n                        '-vframes', '1', '-q:v', '5', '-s', '320x180', str(thumb_file)\n                    ], capture_output=True, timeout=10,\n                    creationflags=subprocess.CREATE_NO_WINDOW if hasattr(subprocess, 'CREATE_NO_WINDOW') else 0)\n                except Exception:\n                    pass  # 缩略图生成失败不影响主流程\n\n            # 生成元数据\n            meta_file = filepath.with_suffix('.meta.json')\n            if not meta_file.exists():\n                try:\n                    result = subprocess.run([\n                        'ffprobe', '-v', 'quiet', '-print_format', 'json',\n                        '-show_format', '-show_streams', str(filepath)\n                    ], capture_output=True, timeout=10,\n                    creationflags=subprocess.CREATE_NO_WINDOW if hasattr(subprocess, 'CREATE_NO_WINDOW') else 0)\n                    if result.returncode == 0:\n                        info = json.loads(result.stdout)\n                        meta = {\"type\": \"video\"}\n                        for s in info.get('streams', []):\n                            if s.get('codec_type') == 'video':\n                                meta['width'] = s.get('width', 0)\n                                meta['height'] = s.get('height', 0)\n                                break\n                        dur = float(info.get('format', {}).get('duration', 0))\n                        h, m = divmod(int(dur), 3600)\n                        m, s = divmod(m, 60)\n                        meta['duration'] = f\"{h:02d}:{m:02d}:{s:02d}\"\n                        meta['duration_sec'] = int(dur)\n                        meta_file.write_text(json.dumps(meta, ensure_ascii=False), encoding='utf-8')\n                except Exception:\n                    pass  # 元数据生成失败不影响主流程\n\n        return {\"success\": True, \"filepath\": str(filepath), \"filename\": file.filename}\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": str(e)}","oldText":"@api_router.post(\"/files/upload-record\", summary=\"接收浏览器上传的录像文件,保存到配置路径。\", tags=[\"Files\"])\nasync def upload_record(request: Request) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"v7.108: 接收浏览器上传的录像文件,保存到配置路径。\"\"\"\n    from pathlib import Path\n    from datetime import datetime\n    from fastapi import UploadFile\n    import shutil\n\n    try:\n        form = await request.form()\n        file: UploadFile = form.get(\"file\")\n        if not file:\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"未收到文件\"}\n\n        record_path = _resolve_storage_path()\n        date_str = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n        date_dir = Path(record_path) / date_str\n        date_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n        filepath = date_dir / file.filename\n        with open(filepath, \"wb\") as f:\n            shutil.copyfileobj(file.file, f)\n\n        return {\"success\": True, \"filepath\": str(filepath), \"filename\": file.filename}\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": str(e)}"}],"path":"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":64800,"output":1378,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783353083968,"responseId":"cht000d9679@dx19f382091492872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb39cbe9","parentId":"5332c6a5","timestamp":"2026-07-06T15:52:08.078Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_66b5673c2c7545fb98a43c5f","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in astrohub\\\\src\\\\api\\\\router.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\r\\nAstroHub v2.0 - 统一路由聚合\\r\\n\\r\\n整合 M1-M11 所有模块路由到 /api/v1/ 下:\\r\\n- /api/v1/health            - 全局健康检查\\r\\n- /api/v1/discovery/sadp    - SADP 设备发现\\r\\n- /api/v1/devices/*         - 设备管理(真实)\\r\\n- /api/v1/ptz/*             - PTZ 控制(真实)\\r\\n- /api/v1/streams/*         - 流服务\\r\\n- /api/v1/calibration/*     - 校准\\r\\n- /api/v1/ascom/*           - ASCOM 设备\\r\\n- /api/v1/settings          - 系统设置\\r\\n\\r\\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\\r\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\r\\n\\r\\nimport asyncio\\r\\nimport time\\r\\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\\r\\nfrom typing import Any\\r\\n\\r\\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\\r\\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI, Query\\r\\nfrom fastapi.responses import JSONResponse, Response, StreamingResponse\\r\\n\\r\\n# v6.40: 操作日志\\r\\nfrom src.operation_logger import log_api, log_web, log_error, log_info\\r\\n\\r\\n# ==========================\\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n\"\"\"\r\nAstroHub v2.0 - 统一路由聚合\r\n\r\n整合 M1-M11 所有模块路由到 /api/v1/ 下:\r\n- /api/v1/health            - 全局健康检查\r\n- /api/v1/discovery/sadp    - SADP 设备发现\r\n- /api/v1/devices/*         - 设备管理(真实)\r\n- /api/v1/ptz/*             - PTZ 控制(真实)\r\n- /api/v1/streams/*         - 流服务\r\n- /api/v1/calibration/*     - 校准\r\n- /api/v1/ascom/*           - ASCOM 设备\r\n- /api/v1/settings          - 系统设置\r\n\r\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import annotations\r\n\r\nimport asyncio\r\nimport time\r\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\r\nfrom typing import Any\r\n\r\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\r\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI, Query\r\nfrom fastapi.responses import JSONResponse, Response, StreamingResponse\r\n\r\n# v6.40: 操作日志\r\nfrom src.operation_logger import log_api, log_web, log_error, log_info\r\n\r\n# ==========================\n... (truncated)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783353128078}}
