{"type":"message","id":"29c0bbd2","parentId":"17dd64ef","timestamp":"2026-07-06T16:49:04.546Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_660a7da546ef41c2a8aa72dc","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":3990,"path":"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":89716,"output":33,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89749,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783356501536,"responseId":"cht000ddc80@dx19f385547682872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5876791","parentId":"29c0bbd2","timestamp":"2026-07-06T16:49:04.552Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_660a7da546ef41c2a8aa72dc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    \"\"\"获取临时目录并确保存在。\"\"\"\r\n    d = os.path.join(_TEMP_ROOT, category, device_ip.replace(\".\", \"_\"))\r\n    os.makedirs(d, exist_ok=True)\r\n    return d\r\n\r\n\r\ndef _cleanup_temp(category: str, device_ip: str):\r\n    \"\"\"清理指定设备指定类别的临时文件。\"\"\"\r\n    import shutil\r\n    d = os.path.join(_TEMP_ROOT, category, device_ip.replace(\".\", \"_\"))\r\n    if os.path.exists(d):\r\n        shutil.rmtree(d, ignore_errors=True)\r\n\r\n\r\ndef _capture_and_crop(client, mgr, device_ip: str, category: str,\r\n                      x: float, y: float, w: float, h: float) -> tuple:\r\n    \"\"\"ISAPI 截图 → 按比例裁剪 → 返回 (bgr, 截图路径, 裁剪信息dict)。\r\n\r\n    统一入口，白平衡和对焦共用。\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import time as _time\r\n    from src.controlpanel.region_base import calc_stable_delay\r\n    delay = calc_stable_delay(client)\r\n    _time.sleep(delay)  # v8.44: 统一延时\r\n    jpg = client.capture_picture()\r\n    if not jpg:\r\n        return None, \"\", {\"error\": \"ISAPI截图失败\"}\r\n\r\n    # 保存全图\r\n    ts = int(_time.time() * 1000)\r\n    temp_dir = _temp_dir(category, device_ip)\r\n    full_path = os.path.join(temp_dir, f\"full_{ts}.jpg\")\r\n    with open(full_path, \"wb\") as f:\r\n        f.write(jpg)\r\n\r\n    bgr = cv2.imdecode(np.frombuffer(jpg, np.uint8), cv2.IMREAD_COLOR)\r\n    if bgr is None:\r\n        return None, full_path, {\"error\": \"图像解码失败\"}\r\n\r\n    full_h, full_w = bgr.shape[:2]\r\n\r\n    # 裁剪\r\n    if w > 0 and h > 0:\r\n        x1 = max(0, int(x * full_w))\r\n        y1 = max(0, int(y * full_h))\r\n        x2 = min(full_w, int((x + w) * full_w))\r\n        y2 = min(full_h, int((y + h) * full_h))\r\n        if x2 <= x1 or y2 <= y1:\r\n            return bgr, full_path, {\"error\": \"裁剪区域无效\"}\r\n        cropped = bgr[y1:y2, x1:x2]\r\n        crop_path = os.path.join(temp_dir, f\"crop_{ts}.jpg\")\r\n        cv2.imwrite(crop_path, cropped)\r\n    else:\r\n        cropped = bgr\r\n        crop_path = full_path\r\n        x1, y1, x2, y2 = 0, 0, full_w, full_h\r\n\r\n    info = {\r\n        \"full_w\": full_w, \"full_h\": full_h,\r\n        \"crop_x1\": x1, \"crop_y1\": y1, \"crop_x2\": x2, \"crop_y2\": y2,\r\n\n[270 more lines in file. Use offset=4050 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783356544551}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ff19526","parentId":"a5876791","timestamp":"2026-07-06T16:51:24.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在的进度：\n1. ✅ 查看了主控台光圈快门实时读取逻辑\n2. ✅ 发现实时读取在 startPtzImagePoll 函数（第1965行），每1秒调用一次 /api/v1/ptz/{ip}/image/iris 和 /api/v1/ptz/{ip}/image/shutter\n3. ✅ 光圈数值映射问题：loadIiris 中有 f-num 映射（numVal/100）\n4. ✅ 查看了所有截图功能位置：\n   - console.html: consoleSnapshot() → /api/v1/ptz/{ip}/capture (主控台截图)\n   - index.html: consoleSnapshot() → 同一条路由\n   - advanced.html: captureAndSolve() → /api/v1/calibrate/capture (校准截图)\n   - router.py: /ptz/{device_id}/capture (ISAPI截图)\n   - _capture_and_crop() (白平衡/对焦的截图函数)\n\n问题1的完整报告：\n- 实时读取逻辑存在（每1秒轮询），但可能有问题\n- 光圈数值映射已存在（1600 → F16.0），但老板说显示为200，说明可能：\n  1. f-num映射代码没生效\n  2. 或者设备返回的 current_level 本身就是200，需要映射到F2.0\n\n问题2的完整报告：\n- 有两处截图入口都指向同一个API：consoleSnapshot() 在console.html和index.html中都有定义！\n- 这就是重复的代码！\n- 不同用途：advanced.html的截图是用于校准的，console.html的截图是用于主控台实际截图的\n \n建议立即修复代码重复问题，确保f-num映射正确。需要统一截图函数，避免多处调用相同接口。同时检查实时读取机制是否存在性能或准确性问题。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板找到了两个问题，我现在整理成报告：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 问题检查报告\n\n### 问题1：光圈快门数值不更新 + 映射问题\n\n**实时读取逻辑存在**（console.html:1965-2021）：\n```javascript\nfunction startPtzImagePoll() {\n    // 每1秒轮询设备参数\n    setInterval(function() {\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n        if (!dev) return;\n\n        // 4. 光圈\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/iris').then(function(r) {\n            var ir = r.data;\n            var iEl = document.getElementById('ptzIris');\n            if (iEl) iEl.textContent = ir.current_level || '--';  // ← 问题：直接显示原始值\n        });\n\n        // 5. 快门\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/shutter').then(function(r) {\n            var sh = r.data;\n            var sEl = document.getElementById('ptzShutter');\n            if (sEl) sEl.textContent = sh.current_level || '--';  // ← 问题：直接显示原始值\n        });\n    }, 1000);\n}\n```\n\n**光圈f-num映射已存在但可能不生效**（console.html:1126-1137）：\n```javascript\nirisValues.forEach(function(val) {\n    var numVal = parseInt(val);\n    var opt = document.createElement('option');\n    opt.value = numVal;\n    var fNum = numVal / 100;\n    opt.textContent = 'F' + fNum.toFixed(1);  // ← 只有选项文本有f-num\n    // ...\n    if (numVal === current) opt.selected = true;\n});\n```\n\n**问题根因**：\n1. ✅ 实时轮询存在，但 `ptzIris` 和 `ptzShutter` 直接显示 `current_level`（原始值，如 200）\n2. ✅ f-num映射只在 `irisLevel` 选项中出现，但 `ptzIris` 只显示原始数值\n3. ✅ 需要转换为F-num显示：200 → `F2.0`\n\n---\n\n### 问题2：截图功能重复\n\n**重复代码位置**：\n1. `astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html` (第1839行) - consoleSnapshot()\n2. `astrohub/src/web/index.html` (第1840行) - consoleSnapshot()\n\n**完全重复**！两个文件中都是：\n```javascript\nfunction consoleSnapshot() {\n    if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n        return;\n    }\n    var deviceIp = window.connectedDevice.ip;\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnConsoleSnapshot');\n    btn.disabled = true;\n    btn.textContent = '抓取中...';\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/capture', null).then(function(result) {\n        // ...\n    });\n}\n```\n\n**三个截图入口**：\n| 位置 | 功能 | API端点 | 是否重复 |\n|------|------|---------|---------|\n| console.html | consoleSnapshot()（主控台截图） | /api/v1/ptz/{ip}/capture | 如果在index.html也有，就是**重复代码** |\n| index.html | consoleSnapshot()（主控台截图） | /api/v1/ptz/{ip}/capture | 与console.html**重复** |\n| advanced.html | captureAndSolve()（校准截图） | /api/v1/calibrate/capture | 不重复 |\n\n**建议**：删除index.html中的consoleSnapshot，因为console.html已经包含了。老板，报告结束了。发现两个问题：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 问题1：光圈快门数值不更新 + 映射问题\n\n**实时读取存在**（console.html:1965-2021），每1秒轮询：\n```javascript\napiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/iris').then(function(r) {\n    var ir = r.data;\n    var iEl = document.getElementById('ptzIris');\n    if (iEl) iEl.textContent = ir.current_level || '--';  // ← 显示原始值200→‘200’\n});\n```\n\n**光圈f-num映射已存在**（console.html:1126）：\n```javascript\nvar fNum = numVal / 100;  // 1600 → 16.0 → 'F16.0'\nopt.textContent = 'F' + fNum.toFixed(1);\n```\n\n**问题**：\n1. ✅ 实时轮询存在，但 `ptzIris` 只显示 `current_level` 原始值（200）→ user看到“200”\n2. ✅ 需要转换为F-num显示：200 → `F2.0`\n\n---\n\n## 📋 问题2：截图功能重复\n\n**重复代码位置**：\n| 文件 | 行数 | 功能 | API端点 |\n|------|------|------|---------|\n| console.html | 1839 | consoleSnapshot() | /ptz/{ip}/capture |\n| index.html | 1840 | **consoleSnapshot()** | /ptz/{ip}/capture |\n\n**完全重复**！两个文件中的 `consoleSnapshot` 函数逻辑一模一样。\n\n**建议**：删除index.html中的consoleSnapshot（外来文件定义），统一使用console.html。\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 需要修复吗？\n\n1. ✅ 实时读取有无更新？→ 需要检查设备的current_level是否真的变了\n2. ✅ f-num映射需要修改 → ptzIris/ptzShutter也要显示F-num\n3. ✅ 删除index.html中的consoleSnapshot重复代码"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":90708,"output":1626,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783356544553,"responseId":"cht000d7281@dx19f38559bff29c2503"}}
