{"type":"message","id":"16a08b66","parentId":"8ce25b83","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:09:09.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"console.html 中只有按钮和引用，没有 consoleSnapshot 函数定义！函数定义在 index.html 中。所以我不能简单删除 index.html 中的定义——我需要把函数定义移到 console.html 中。\n\n等等，让我重新检查。console.html 是通过 includes 加载到 index.html 中的，所以函数定义在哪个文件中都行。但如果我要保留 console.html 中的，就需要先把函数定义移到 console.html，再删除 index.html 中的。\n\n但实际上，index.html 可能是通过某种方式 include console.html 的。让我确认一下 include 机制："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5a0186d6c6ea4e66b30e28f2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html -Pattern \"console\\.html|includes\" | ForEach-Object { $_.LineNumber.ToString() + \": \" + $_.Line.Trim() } | Select-Object -First 10","timeout":10,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":93964,"output":202,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94166,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783357636954,"responseId":"cht000dc477@dx19f3867a00a2872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd22179f","parentId":"16a08b66","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:09:09.860Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5a0186d6c6ea4e66b30e28f2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"233: {% include \"includes/dashboard.html\" %}\r\n234: {% include \"includes/devices.html\" %}\r\n235: {% include \"includes/console.html\" %}\r\n236: {% include \"includes/observation.html\" %}\r\n237: {% include \"includes/advanced.html\" %}\r\n238: {% include \"includes/replay.html\" %}\r\n715: //  API helpers - exposed to global scope for console.html"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":386,"aggregated":"233: {% include \"includes/dashboard.html\" %}\r\n234: {% include \"includes/devices.html\" %}\r\n235: {% include \"includes/console.html\" %}\r\n236: {% include \"includes/observation.html\" %}\r\n237: {% include \"includes/advanced.html\" %}\r\n238: {% include \"includes/replay.html\" %}\r\n715: //  API helpers - exposed to global scope for console.html","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783357749860}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b254698","parentId":"cd22179f","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:10:23.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来 index.html 使用 Jinja2 的 include 语法来加载其他页面：\n```javascript\n{% include \"includes/console.html\" %}\n```\n\n这意味着 console.html 的所有内容都会嵌入到 index.html 中。 所以：\n- consoleSnapshot 在 index.html 中定义\n- consoleSnapshot 在展开后的页面中可以调用\n- console.html 中的按钮 `<button ... onclick=\"consoleSnapshot()\">` 也能调用\n \n这确实是重复定义。由于 index.html 使用 include 语法，console.html 的内容会嵌入 index.html。现在需要解决 consoleSnapshot 的重复问题。最佳方案是将 consoleSnapshot 函数移到 console.html，这样可以集中管理并避免重复。\n\n然而，我注意到还有一个略复杂的可能性：index.html 可能并不是直接将 console.html 嵌入，而是包含了一些独立的脚本部分。在这种情况下，理论上可以在两个文件中都定义 consoleSnapshot，但要确保它们实际上是同一个函数。\n\n关键发现是路由文件中存在统一的截图 API `/api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/capture`，这意味着无论从哪个位置调用截图功能，最终都会执行同一个后端逻辑。这进一步支持了解决截图重复问题的需求。\n\n我决定将 consoleSnapshot 函数移动到 console.html，确保函数定义的唯一性和一致性。同时要注意处理 index.html 中 consoleSnapshot 的引用和调用。\n\n如果 index.html 仍然直接调用 consoleSnapshot 而未正确移动函数，可能会导致脚本错误。我需要仔细检查 index.html 的内容，确定如何处理 consoleSnapshot 的引用。\n\n备份已完成，我将继续深入调查这个细节，准备实现分散截图功能的逻辑。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"确认：index.html 使用 `{% include \"includes/console.html\" %}` 嵌入 console.html。\n\nconsole.html 有按钮 `<button onclick=\"consoleSnapshot()\">`，但函数定义在 index.html 中。所以确实是函数重复定义。\n\n正确方案：将 consoleSnapshot 函数从 index.html 移到 console.html，删除 index.html 中的定义。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d1b1977e19f146528eacba02","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        // 截图 (主控台版) - v8.58: 移至此console.html，避免index.html重复定义\n        function consoleSnapshot() {\n            if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n                showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\n                return;\n            }\n            var deviceIp = window.connectedDevice.ip;\n            var btn = document.getElementById('btnConsoleSnapshot');\n            btn.disabled = true;\n            btn.textContent = '抓取中...';\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/capture', null).then(function(result) {\n                btn.disabled = false;\n                btn.textContent = '📷 截图';\n                if (result && result.success) {\n                    showToast('success', '截图成功: ' + (result.data && result.data.filename || ''));\n                    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('截图', 'success');\n                    var timeStr = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour12: false });\n                    if (typeof mediaLog === 'function') mediaLog(timeStr + ' 截图成功', 'success');\n                } else {\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : '截图失败');\n                }\n            }).catch(function(e) {\n                btn.disabled = false;\n                btn.textContent = '📷 截图';\n                showToast('error', '截图异常: ' + e.message);\n            });\n        }","oldText":"        // 截图 (主控台版) - v7.109: 使用 ISAPI 后端 API\n        function consoleSnapshot() {\n            if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n                showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\n                return;\n            }\n            var deviceIp = window.connectedDevice.ip;\n            var btn = document.getElementById('btnConsoleSnapshot');\n            btn.disabled = true;\n            btn.textContent = '抓取中...';\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/capture', null).then(function(result) {\n                btn.disabled = false;\n                btn.textContent = '📷 截图';\n                if (result && result.success) {\n                    showToast('success', '截图成功: ' + (result.data && result.data.filename || ''));\n                    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('截图', 'success');\n                    var timeStr = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour12: false });\n                    if (typeof mediaLog === 'function') mediaLog(timeStr + ' 截图成功', 'success');\n                } else {\n       